GAUTENG Education MEC Panyaza Lesufi is vacating the office,
as he announced that Friday is his last day in office. The MEC said: “Bidding farewell to the education team.” HE further said: “Thank you so much for the hard work Team
Gauteng Education. The education sector is now in a better shape. Proud to hand
over the baton to conclude the remaining tasks #GautengEducation.” According to Lesufi he is vacating office due to the end of
the political term. Meanwhile, many took to social media to acknowledge the good
work he has done for the education department in Gauteng.  